div.p:
To the People in general, I have only this comprehenſive Word to offer, Be dutiful and obedient to your Civil Fathers, and at Peace among yourſelves. Forget not the Words of our bleſſed Saviour, Every Kingdom divided againſt itſelf is brought to Deſolation;


                  and every City or Houſe divided againſt itſelf ſhall not ſtand 
                  Matth. 12.25..
